         <dc:description>
            <rdf:Alt>
               <rdf:li xml:lang="x-default">Cute red squirrel set. Fluffy cartoon animal with furry tail holding nut, jumping, moving. Flat vector illustrations for wildlife, mammals, forest fauna, adorable character concept</rdf:li>
